---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="konbu — パーソナルワークスペース" description="メモ・ToDo・カレンダー・ツールをひとつに。無料で使えるオープンソースのワークスペース。">
  <!-- Header -->
  <header class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 border-b border-zinc-800/50 bg-zinc-950/80 backdrop-blur-sm">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 h-14 flex items-center justify-between">
      <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="konbu" class="w-6 h-6" />
        <span class="font-semibold text-lg">konbu</span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://github.com/krtw00/konbu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-sm text-zinc-400 hover:text-zinc-100 transition-colors">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://konbu-cloud.codenica.dev" class="text-sm font-medium bg-white text-zinc-900 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-md hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors">
          使ってみる
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">
        メモ・ToDo・カレンダーを<br />
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-400 to-teal-400">ひとつに</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-400 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        konbu はシンプルなパーソナルワークスペース。<br />
        日々のメモ、タスク、予定をひとつの場所で管理できます。
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-3">
        <a href="https://konbu-cloud.codenica.dev" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-zinc-900 font-medium px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors">
          無料で始める
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/krtw00/konbu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-300 font-medium px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-colors">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-16">
      <img src="/hero.png" alt="konbu ダッシュボード" class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 shadow-2xl shadow-emerald-500/5" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Features -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-zinc-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-12">シンプルで必要十分な機能</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8Z"/><path d="M14 2v6h6"/><path d="M16 13H8"/><path d="M16 17H8"/><path d="M10 9H8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">メモ</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">Markdown対応。タグ付き、ライブプレビュー、画像添付。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-blue-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">ToDo</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">期限・ステータス管理。クイック入力でサクサク追加。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect width="18" height="18" x="3" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="M16 2v4"/><path d="M8 2v4"/><path d="M3 10h18"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">カレンダー</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">月表示カレンダー。予定の作成・編集がワンクリック。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-orange-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.3-4.3"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">横断検索</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">メモ・ToDo・予定をまとめて即座に検索。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Sponsor Features -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-zinc-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Sponsor 特典</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-10">プロジェクトを支援すると、さらに便利な機能が使えます。</p>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-left">
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1 text-sm">AI チャット</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">自然言語でデータ操作。BYOK対応。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1 text-sm">画像添付</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">メモにドラッグ&ドロップで画像貼り付け。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-5 rounded-xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/50">
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1 text-sm">API / CLI / MCP</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-zinc-400">外部ツールとの連携。Claude Desktop対応。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OSS -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-zinc-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">オープンソース</h2>
      <p class="text-zinc-400 mb-6">
        MIT ライセンス。セルフホストも可能です。<br />
        Go + React + PostgreSQL。
      </p>
      <a href="https://github.com/krtw00/konbu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 border border-zinc-700 text-zinc-300 font-medium px-6 py-2.5 rounded-lg hover:bg-zinc-800 transition-colors">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0 0 24 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
        ソースコードを見る
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="py-8 px-6 border-t border-zinc-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex items-center justify-between text-sm text-zinc-500">
      <span>&copy; 2026 konbu</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/krtw00/konbu" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hover:text-zinc-300">GitHub</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Layout>
